## Testing Strategy

| Layer | What to Test | Approach |
|-------|-------------|----------|
| Unit | Form validation logic | Test Zod schemas with valid/invalid data |
| Unit | Zustand store actions | Test store updates and selectors |
| Unit | Helper functions | Test localStorage and JSON generation utilities |
| Integration | Form component interactions | Test form submission and state updates |
| Integration | Editor page flow | Test complete user flow from input to export |
| E2E | Full editor workflow | Playwright test for complete user journey |

## Migration / Rollout

No migration required. This is a new frontend-only feature.

